  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the hot stone plate to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the borlotti beans, confit tomato, lemon juice, tahini, garlic, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Blend the mixture on high speed until smooth and creamy.",
    "With the blender or food processor running, slowly pour in the olive oil.",
    "Continue blending until the hummus is light and fluffy.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the hummus to a serving bowl and garnish with a sprinkle of smoked paprika.",
    "Serve the hummus on the preheated hot stone plate, garnished with additional confit tomato if desired."
